description:
&lt;p&gt;We currently have a vacancy for a Band 3 Senior Support Worker to join our team at Kingscroft Short Break Service for adults with Learning Disabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should have experience of working with adults with learning disabilities, be enthusiastic, an effective communicator, have high standards, and be sensitive to the needs of people with learning disabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NVQ level 3 in health and social care or equivalent training is required. Working hours are 37.5 hours per week, and the willingness to work flexible including; varied shifts, weekends and nights essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal enquiry regarding the post please contact: Louise Nicholson on 01784 465134. We look forward to your application.&lt;/p&gt;
